The OSIRIS setup has been optimized for the purpose to detect the residuals of natural U/Th contamination of the LS. It will hold a 18-ton sample of LS enclosed in an Acrylic Vessel (AV) for screening, surrounded by an extensive water shield. The search is based on the fast coincidence decays of 214\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
