				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$1\sigma $$\end{document}, cf. Table 1), about 2×103\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$2\times 10^3$$\end{document} s.p.e. pulses are required to reach a relative timing alignment of 25 ps (1σ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
