				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$1\sigma $$\end{document}) between channels. Due to the low average light intensity, about 2×105\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
