The Source Insertion System is mounted to the top of the Calibration Flange on the roof of the OSIRIS Water Tank. It is based on an Automated Calibration Unit (ACU), which has been provided by the Daya Bay collaboration [4], and then refurbished to suit OSIRIS’s needs. A 3′′\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
